{"type": "article", "id": 12320, "title": "安抚情绪的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-20T08:13:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607133944peloundqv4IXmOCi.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\">设计师 Dorja Benussi 懂孩子，也懂广大都市年轻人。这款叫做 Soothing Chair 的椅子在普通椅子的基础上加了一个遮光罩，展开的时候像是一个蚕茧，把人包围在里面。软软的椅子背看上去就很“治愈系”，虽然人家设计师号称这是一个儿童座椅，但是感觉对都市的年轻人更加适用呢。你可以坐着办公，蹲着办公，也可以把罩子一拉告诉大家“别来烦我”。</span><a href=\"https://www.behance.net/dorja\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a><span style=\"text-align:justify;\">可以查看 Dorja Benussi 的更多作品。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140104ragqIjblFR3KsM14.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140105KboTtd3GJMfmrIli.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140105pcnMDhBAz4qT1J0t.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261401055Zb1NCOWQ3ozgwxm.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140106aT3ztPH4fxAWGZci.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140107CXUQ3RvGqnkjlyNf.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}